Only for the delivery tracking plugin between McDelivery to Barogo.

This extension makes it easy to request delivery to the Barogo Store from the *OQM. 
When you request a delivery in the OQM order list, this extension supports automatically fills the Barogo order form using a OQM order detail information.
*OQM = McDelivery Order Queue Manager
